      %p.font-20.margin-top-20.margin-bottom-20
        The field is a regulation sized indoor soccer field with full sized goals. The turf field is walled so the ball is in play all the time (no side-line or corner hits). The venue allows a unique fast/indoor hockey experience in an outdoor setting.
      %h3.font-32.margin-bottom-20
        Additional Information
      %p.font-20.margin-top-20.margin-bottom-20
        A social/mixed team must have at least 2 women players on the field or the team shall play short of women player(s). Women may participate in Men/Competition division.
      %p.font-20.margin-top-20.margin-bottom-20
        The host club will provide refreshments and food for guest team members throughout the tournament, and a casual dinner is planned for Saturday night. Dinner event participation is free for registered team members. Additional persons are $15 each.

